flowchart LR
    subgraph Write [Write path]
        P[Post created] --> FS[Fan-out / graph]
        FS --> Cache[Per-user feed cache]
        FS --> Idx[Search / index optional]
    end
    subgraph Read [Read path]
        R[GET /feed] --> Rank[Ranking]
        Cache --> Rank
        Rank --> Resp[JSON + cursors]
    end
